DateTime::Format::Mail

   Convert between DateTime and RFC2822/822 formats

For installation details, see INSTALL.

For usage, see the doco. Either use perldoc or view it
on the web at:
    <http://search.cpan.org/author/SPOON/DateTime-Format-Mail/>

Changes for 0.24 (8 Apr 2003)
   - Minor documentation fixes.
   - Refactored year and timezone repair functions.
   - Added tests for said functions.
   - Added ability to parse multiple sign timezones.
   - GMT and UTC are recognised as timezone names.

For a complete list of changes, see the Changes file.


by Iain Truskett.
